de.tuhh.diss.harborstorage.sim

Interface StoragePlace


  • public interface StoragePlace
    This interface abstracts a storage place (i.e. a slot within the high rack) where a storage element can be stored. It contains methods to get information about the size, the location and the number of such a storage place.
    Author:
    Weigel
